Groovy tutorial: https://leanpub.com/groovytutorial/read
Groovy AST: https://www.mo4tech.com/groovy-ast.html
Executing Groovy Scripts in a Maven Build: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rDv2c13j3vg
